test_odd_range:
assert [121] == [121, 121]
  Right contains one more item: 121
  Full diff:
  - [121, 121]
  + [121]
test_all_one_range:
assert [1] == [1, 1]
  Right contains one more item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1]
  + [1]
test_all_negative_ones:
assert [-1] == [-1, -1]
  Right contains one more item: -1
  Full diff:
  - [-1, -1]
  + [-1]
